How you can help
===============================
 * use it
 * [report bugs](https://bugs.launchpad.net/ndisgtk/) you found.
 * If you can, please help [translating ndisgtk](https://translations.launchpad.net/ndisgtk/trunk/+pots/ndisgtk/).
 * Tell others about it
 * package it for your distribution (except for Debian and Ubuntu, as I'm doing this).

Distribution packages
===============================
 * [Debian](http://packages.debian.org/ndisgtk)
 * [Ubuntu](http://packages.ubuntu.com/ndisgtk)
 * [openSUSE/SUSE](http://software.opensuse.org/search?q=ndisgtk&amp;p=1&amp;baseproject=ALL)
 * [Wolvix](http://wolvix.org/) (Included on disk)
 * [RedHat Enterprise Linux (3,4,5) and compatible](http://dag.wieers.com/rpm/packages/ndisgtk/)
 * [Paldo](http://www.paldo.org/index.php?section=packages&page=main&query=ndisgtk)
 * [Slackware (linuxpackages.net)](http://www.linuxpackages.net/search_view.php?by=name&name=ndisgtk&ver=)
 * [Zenwalk (official repo)](http://zenwalk.linuxish.net/i486/current/xap/)
 * [Zenwalk (latest release)](http://zenwalk.linuxish.net/i486/snapshot/xap/)


